<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ر د أ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٠٧٤ - ر د أ]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ردَأَ يَردَأ، رَدْءًا، فهو رادئ، والمفعول مَرْدوء<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• ردَأ الحائطَ:</span> دعَمه وقوَّاه <span class="c1">"ردَأ مبنًى"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• ردَأ الشَّخصَ:</span> أعانه <span class="c1">"ردَأ مسكينًا/ فقيرًا"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• ردَأه بحجرٍ:</span> رماه به.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>